description: קובץ מדיה שהתקבל מהמשתמש (שמי הוא דביר Dvir دبير)

A high-quality 3-panel meme using the Vince McMahon reaction template, showing his escalating excitement for different representations of complex numbers. Panel 1: Vince McMahon with a neutral, unimpressed expression next to the text 'z = a + bi'. Panel 2: Vince McMahon leaning forward with interest next to the text 'z = r(cosθ + isinθ)'. Panel 3: Vince McMahon leaning back, mind-blown with extreme excitement, next to the text 'z = r·e^(iθ)'. The text should be white with a black outline for maximum readability against any background.
